2月7日凌晨，武汉市中心医院发布消息，“被训诫武汉医生”李文亮于2月7日2点58分不幸逝世。
In the early morning hours of Feb. 7, Wuhan city central hospital announced that the "admonished Wuhan doctor" Li Wenliang died at 2: 58 on February 7.
2月8日16时39分，李文亮妻子的认证微博账号@付雪洁 发声明称，截至2月8日16时，其收到四个渠道依法依规应给予赔付的部分款项；未收到其他任何个人或团体机构的捐助款项。
On 8 February, at 1639 hours, Li Wenliang's wife's certified Weibo account @ Fu Xuejie issued a statement stating that, as at 1600 hours on 8 February, it had received four legally required partial payments; no contributions had been received from any other individual or group of individuals.
同时，其表示“本人未发布任何性质的求助信息，也未授权其他人员发布相关信息或接受捐助。
At the same time, it said that "I have not published any kind of help information, nor authorized other personnel to publish relevant information or accept donations."
”在2月8日的公开《声明》中，李文亮妻子付雪洁就近期网上关于李文亮家属接收捐款或捐助的信息进行回应。
In a public statement on February 8, Li Wenliang's wife, Fu Xuejie, responded to recent online information about donations or donations received by Li's family.
《声明》称，其仅接受四个渠道的款项，分别是“国家依法依规给予李文亮工伤、丧葬等有关的赔付项款；李文亮工作单位（武汉市中心医院）和本人工作单位（武汉爱尔眼科医院）的帮助款项；李文亮生前依法购买保险的赔付款项；政府部门认可或授权的公益单位（含保险）依法设定给予全体抗击疫情医务人员范畴内的公益基金或奖励，属于李文亮作为医务人员依法享有的部分款项”等。
Li Wenliang's work unit (Wuhan Er Eye Hospital) and his work unit (Wuhan Er Eye Hospital) paid for the insurance according to law; public welfare units (including insurance) approved or authorized by government departments to provide public funds or awards to all medical personnel fighting the epidemic are part of the funds Li was entitled to as a medical worker according to law.
据《声明》，截至2020年2月8日16时，其收到上述渠道依法依规应给予赔付的部分款项；未收到其他任何个人或团体机构的捐助款项。
According to the Statement, as at 1600 hours on 8 February 2020, it had received part of the payments due under the law from the above-mentioned channels; no contributions had been received from any other individual or group of institutions.
同时，其表示，“坚持拒绝接受除上述渠道以外任何形式的个人或团体机构的款项或捐助”。
At the same time, it said, "persistent refusal to accept any form of money or contributions from individuals or organizations other than the above-mentioned channels."
此外，《声明》也显示，“近期网上发布的各类涉及对李文亮的捐助信息均由发布人自行发布，本人未予以认可，且与本人无任何关系。
In addition, the Statement also showed that "all kinds of information published recently on the Internet concerning donations to Li Wenliang have been published by the publishers themselves, without my approval and without any personal connection."
本人未发布任何性质的求助信息，也未授权其他人员发布相关信息或接受捐助。
I do not publish any help information of any nature, nor do I authorize others to post relevant information or accept donations.
”2月7日凌晨，武汉市中心医院发布消息，该院眼科医生李文亮，在抗击新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情工作中不幸感染，经全力抢救无效，于2月7日凌晨2点58分去世，该院深表痛惜和哀悼。
In the early morning hours of February 7, Wuhan Central Hospital announced that Li Wenliang, an ophthalmologist at the hospital, had died at 2.58 a.m. on February 7 after suffering an unfortunate infection in the battle against pneumonia infected with a new coronavirus.
2月7日，经中央批准，国家监察委员会派出调查组赴湖北省武汉市，就群众反映的涉及李文亮医生的有关问题作全面调查。
On February 7, with the approval of the central government, the state supervisory committee sent an investigation team to Wuhan City, Hubei Province, to make a comprehensive investigation into the problems reported by the masses concerning Dr. Li Wenliang.
2月8日，国家监察委员会调查组已抵达武汉。
On 8 February, the investigation team of the State Monitoring Committee arrived in Wuhan.
另据湖北之声、人民日报官微等报道，2月7日，武汉市人社部门认定李文亮作为医护人员在抗击新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情工作中不幸感染并经抢救无效去世，属于工伤。
According to reports from Hubei Sound and People's Daily, on February 7, the Wuhan Bureau of Human Society identified Li Wenliang as a medical worker in the fight against the new coronavirus infection of pneumonia unfortunately infected and died after rescue is an industrial injury.
其工伤保险待遇为一次性工亡补助金78.502万元、丧葬补助金3.6834万元，目前已拨付到位。
His industrial injury insurance benefits of 785.02 million yuan, funeral grant 36.834 million yuan, has been allocated.
